00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.240
I'm the head of the Poetry and
Literature Center and I'm thrilled

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:31.720
to welcome you to this afternoon's
event, celebrating the poetry

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:37.970
of Pablo Neruda and featuring
Forrest Gander and Marjorie Agosín.

00:00:37.970 --> 00:00:40.810
First, let me ask you to
do what I'm going to do,

00:00:40.810 --> 00:00:47.580
