this program is being recorded

00:00:55.790 --> 00:01:01.340
and by participating, you give us
for future use of the recording.

00:01:01.340 --> 00:01:06.430
Tonight's event is cosponsored by
the library's Hispanic division

00:01:06.430 --> 00:01:08.370
and the Poetry and
Literature Center.

