years ago in Spain, Latin America,

00:11:08.980 --> 00:11:12.960 position:56%
I thought, "Oh, they're just
squeezing stuff Neruda really didn't

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:17.010
want to have published and
making a dollar on it."

00:11:17.010 --> 00:11:22.040
And then I saw the reviews and
the reviews were startling good

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:27.870
and then I had the opportunity
to translate the work and looked

00:11:27.870 --> 00:11:31.800
